# Backend Python Rules

- Use async SQLAlchemy sessions via `get_db` dependency
- All routes mounted under `/api/v1/` prefix in `app/main.py`
- Pydantic schemas live in `app/api/schemas.py`
- New scrapers: inherit `JobSource`, implement `fetch()`, register in `app/services/scraper_runner.py`
- Handle scraper failures gracefully — return empty list, never crash the runner
- Deduplication uses SHA-256 hash of normalized title+company (`get_dedup_hash`)
